-- Account computer:
--   ID 8166
--   rednet protocol "casino"
--   modem on bottom
--
-- Changes in this version:
--   - Decorative inner border around dealer area
--   - Player card positions stay perfect, but card/suit orientation flipped back
--   - Station monitors show current hand value under play buttons
